Please follow up with your regular veterinarian to formulate a treatment plan for your new pet.<p/><p/>2)  This animal has been diagnosed as hyperthyroid.  This means that thyroid gland is producing an excess of hormones.  This disease can be easily managed with daily medication, radioactive iodine treatment or prescription diet.  Please follow up with you regular veterinarian to create a treatment plan.  We have also included a handout with more information about this disease.<p/>
